data.description: All of the major updates have been done for you in this 3 bed, 2 bath cape cod located right in the heart of Clintonville. BONUS! This home sits on a half acre lot and is minutes to everything you need including shopping, dining, walking/biking trails, parks, and more. This home has newer mechanicals, windows, and flooring. Open spaces on the first floor make entertaining a breeze and the large stone fireplace has gas logs and remote starter. Renovated kitchen also has newer appliances. First floor primary bedroom is tucked away from the main living areas and updated bathroom features claw foot tub with a tile surround. Upstairs has two bedrooms, full bathroom, and a large landing perfect for study or den. Pull through carport AND a 2 car detached garage. Don't miss out on this huge yard!
